02:12:53.730 --> 02:12:57.118
SAM: You just want to kill everybody.

02:12:57.118 --> 02:12:58.313
TALIESIN: I do.

02:12:58.313 --> 02:13:02.765
MARISHA: I'm going to try Lockheed. His dad could
be in a place where he's being watched.

