LAURA: Jutting out the side of--

02:14:49.293 --> 02:14:53.258
MATT: Yeah. It's not sitting on ground, but is
currently over the ravine.

02:14:53.258 --> 02:15:00.159
MARISHA: Yeah, one of those. Any other trees? Is
