02:16:07.258 --> 02:16:08.599
TALIESIN: Grog first.

02:16:08.599 --> 02:16:15.910
SAM: Should you scry one more time, for the dad?
Because best-case scenario, we're in a weird,

02:16:15.910 --> 02:16:19.426
