02:16:45.964 --> 02:16:48.467
SAM: Seems like a good plan.

02:16:48.467 --> 02:16:49.632
LAURA: This is risky.

02:16:49.632 --> 02:16:51.060
MARISHA: This is ridiculous.

02:16:51.060 --> 02:16:56.696
TALIESIN: It's true. There's only risk at this
