TRAVIS: I do hate to have my own words used
against me.

02:17:43.964 --> 02:17:49.854
SAM: All risk. That's what this is! We are
doing all risk!

02:17:49.854 --> 02:17:57.471
TRAVIS: I'm down to party. I'm just saying it was
